{
  "stem": "5740.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 134,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, at the end, the last few months we worked outside at the-- digging trenches for the Germans.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 134,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was so strong that I sometimes digged the biggest trenches, the biggest pieces out of, of stones out.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 134,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And when the SS man saw it, he gave me a bit of soup.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 135,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So you actually were a, a prize worker again.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 135,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "From being a prize knitter--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 136,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was a prize worker there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 137,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So you, you had the strength and, and the relative health--",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 138,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 139,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To continue.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 140,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 140,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 140,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "All around me, people were dying, but I hadn't seen a corpse.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 141,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the barrack.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 141,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When they, when they-- when somebody was dying on tuberculosis, they took him out already half dead.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 141,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were dying in, in, in, in the sick rooms on, on typhoid, of malnutrition and everything.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 141,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I saw them.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 141,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I saw them.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 141,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I saw people walking like corpses.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 142,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 142,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I remember their name till today.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 142,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't remember their alive names, but the one who died.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 143,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And you somehow did not get typhus, and you did not get tuberculosis.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 144,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I never had a headache.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 145,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So you managed to keep--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 146,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was-- I, I keep-- I keep pretty well.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 147,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no, no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 148,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, I met her in the camp, and I became friendly with her in the camp.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 148,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I knew her maybe by sight because she comes from the same city, but she didn't go to the same school.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 148,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I only knew kids which went to the same school.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 149,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, yes, definitely.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 150,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, we, we, we used to give courage one another.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 150,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I knew that I can depend-- if I get-- if something-- if I, if I be hungry, that she will do anything to give me a scrap of bread.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 150,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It, it was a lot.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
